members.name: getParams
members.comment: Returns the algorithm parameters associated with the key.

name: java.security.interfaces.EdECKey
comment: An interface for an elliptic curve public/private key as defined by RFC 8032: Edwards-Curve Digital Signature Algorithm (EdDSA). These keys are distinct from the keys represented by ECKey, and they are intended for use with algorithms based on RFC 8032 such as the EdDSA Signature algorithm. This interface allows access to the algorithm parameters associated with the key.
